description:
(Part 2 of 7) MONEY plays a large role in the battle between Jesus and Satan. White Horse Medias 7-part series explores the peril and power of money, laziness, working, eliminating debt, saving, tithes and offerings, investing vs. gambling, retirement, and earths final crisis when no man can buy or sell save he that has the mark. Revelation 13:17. Based on Scripture and practical wise principles.
